Package com.mySTARS.Control

com.mySTARS.control is used for control classes handling actions within the system
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountMgr
    Manages account retrieval and backend checking.
    AdminMgr
    Admin manager class that handling of Admin objects
    EncryptionMgr
    This EncryptionMgr class is what is used to mask the passwords that user inputs
    FileMgr
    File manager for handling of data in external files
    NotificationMgr  
    sendEmail
    class for sending of email through api
    SerializationMgr
    Serialization manager to handle serialization and deserialization of data
    SystemMgr
    manages interactions between the boundaries and the system
    UpdateCourseMgr
    Class to handle the updating of course interactions
    UserMgr
    user manager class that handling of student objects
